import {
  Box,
  Flex,
  Heading, 
  Input, 
  Text, 
  InputGroup,
  InputRightElement, 
  Stack,
  Checkbox
} from '@chakra-ui/react';

import { Image } from "@chakra-ui/image";

import "../CSS/Login.css";

import Group from "../imagens/Group.png"

import {  FaLock } from "react-icons/fa"
import { EmailIcon } from "@chakra-ui/icons";
import { FcGoogle  } from "react-icons/fc";

import { Button } from "@chakra-ui/button";

import celular from "../imagens/celular.png"
import Montanhas from "../imagens/montanhas.jpg"


const Login = () => {

  return (
    <Box height="100%">
        <Flex height="100vh" alingItems="center" justifyContent="center"  >
       <Box mt="80px">
       
       <Image  src={Montanhas} height="500px" width="280px" alt="celular"/>
       <Image mt="500px" src={celular} height="500px" width="280px" alt="celular"/>
        <Flex 
        direction="column" 
        height="500px"
        width="270px" 
        borderRadius="35px" 
        mt="-500px"
        ml="5px"
        border="1px"
        borderColor="#FFFFFF"
        >
        
         
      </Flex>  
       </Box>
      </Flex>
    </Box>
  )
}

export default Login;
